{"type": "article", "id": 22191, "title": "蕾哈娜首次带PUMA上纽约时装周，以及，裸色口红也可以很多样｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-02-14T09:55:54Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 20739, "name": "STUSSY"}, {"id": 17505, "name": "Outdoor Voices"}, {"id": 1297, "name": "阿迪达斯"}, {"id": 6839, "name": "Christian Dior"}, {"id": 17749, "name": "yeezy"}, {"id": 1686, "name": "Marc Jacobs"}, {"id": 1576, "name": "欧莱雅"}, {"id": 2182, "name": "康泰纳仕"}, {"id": 6459, "name": "雅芳"}, {"id": 23303, "name": "Future Glory"}, {"id": 23304, "name": "Star Jewelry"}, {"id": 1722, "name": "Alexander Wang"}, {"id": 2968, "name": "Mulberry"}, {"id": 3194, "name": "Air Force"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 75588, "comment_count": 12, "praise_count": 98, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607131851FQ5i9bNW4tGcvgaf.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><b><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Christian-Dior-2015-profits-up-33-to-4-07-billion-euros,655610.html#.Vr9RVYRVfBI\">Christian Dior 2015 年收益降低 33%</a>｜</b>法国奢侈品牌 Christian Dior 近日财报显示 2015 年度净利润达到 40.7 亿欧元，与去年的 61.2 亿欧元相比减少了 33%。收入表现最佳的部门为钟表和珠宝部门，增长了 19%（现汇率）达到了 33 亿欧元，紧接着是 Dior 高定，增长了 17% 至 18.7 亿。</p>\n<p><b><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/L-Oreal-fourth-quarter-sales-growth-beats-forecasts,655181.html#.Vr9RcoRVfBI\">欧莱雅四季度销售额增长超预期</a>｜</b>法国美妆巨头欧莱雅（L’Oreal）集团四季度获得了超出预期的销售额，有赖于美国境内的稳健增长，和其奢侈产品的弹性需求。截至 12 月 31 日的过去三个月，其旗下的兰蔻（Lancome）面霜和圣罗兰（Yves Saint Laurent）香水的收入获得了 4.2% 的增长，超过了分析师 3.6% 的预期。全年营业利润上涨了 12.8% 达到 43.9 亿欧元（约 49.8 亿美元）。</p>\n<p><b><a href=\"http://www.racked.com/2016/2/12/10978762/w-magazine-digital-conde-nast\">康泰纳仕集团旗下 W 杂志组建新线上团队</a>｜</b>W 杂志任命了新的行政数字总监、联合新闻主编、副数字编辑、数字文化编辑和数码图片编辑。前康泰纳仕娱乐行政高管 Jun Harada 担任行政数字总监，新的联合新闻主编 Ally Betker 则来自 WWD，New York  杂志线上网站 The Cut 的编辑助理 Stephanie Eckardt 担任新的副数字编辑，剩下的数字文化和图片编辑都来自 W 杂志内部。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://www.nofashion.cn/a/1455194719678.html\">雅芳连续 16 个季度收入下跌 </a>| </b>雅芳周四盘前发布四季度及 2015 全年财报，公司四季度收入大跌 20.2% 至 16.073 亿美元，连续 16 个季度下跌，撇除 Liz Earle 业务和不利汇率集团号称有 3% 的增幅。该直销公司四季度收入持续萎缩主要受最大市场拉美市场拖累，远逊于 Capital IQ Consensus 预期的 18.2 亿美元。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://www.nofashion.cn/a/1455210275669.html\">Adidas 2015 财年</a> | </b>阿迪达斯集团周四披露 2015 年初步业绩，集团 2015 财年全年收入增长 16% 至 169 亿欧元，固定汇率下增幅 10%，超越市场预期的 167 亿欧元；来自持续经营业务净利润增幅 12% 至 7.20 亿欧元，同样超越市场预期的 7.11 亿欧元。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://www.nofashion.cn/a/1455107166596.html\">Urban Outfitters 四季度财报</a> | </b>净销售为 10.134 亿美元，与上年同期 10.110 亿美元基本持平，略低于华尔街分析师预期的 10.2 亿美元，四季度集团同店销售有 2% 的跌幅，其中 Free People 品牌同店销售有 2% 的增幅，Anthropologie 和Urban Outfitters 则分别下跌 2% 和 3%。<br></p>\n<p><b><a href=\"http://www.vogue.co.uk/news/2016/02/12/mulberry-new-licensing-deal-footwear-and-ready-to-wear\">Mulberry 开始全球分销</a> | </b>品牌日前宣布，已经与日本控股的意大利奢侈品集团 Onward Luxury Group 达成了新的授权协议，将在全球进行成衣和鞋履的分销，这一举措将大大削减时装屋本身的成本开支。</p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\">\r\n\r\n这里有一些纽约时装周上值得一看的秀场图：\r\n\r\n</p>\n<p class=\"\">Fenty x Puma by Rihanna：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131828s6AxTzyicZq4hw8u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"3.76481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">Kanye West 推出 Yeezy 第三季：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131829iqzspR941MtgZjv2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071318296rZEYNfB4xGpdycb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131830Qw0z6bjeB74vPXCa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071318307t9VuelCj5drOMkf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">春天不远了，这里推荐一个很有春天气息的首饰品牌。来自日本的 Star Jewelry，1946 年由 Saburo Nagai 和他的妻子 Taeko Nagai 创立，品牌今年刚好来到第 70 个年头。今年推出了以下这个 Flowers &amp; Leaves 系列。系列已经全面上市，有兴趣的朋友可以到<a href=\"https://spur.hpplus.jp/jewelry_watch/news/201602/07/QGkGUYM/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">官网</a>了解更多。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131831mRPMf24QgBz3w7Nq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071318321MeGqt93dZ4oH2EQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131832a0hJbrPLYUVZRp5x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131833sLfD7yvaVmYSht3k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131833Fg1uZ6HS53CrRhjn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">Nike 推出北极光灵感的 Air Force 1，目前已经上市，定价为 120 美元。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131834AntZi5IaDhk6r2GP.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131835SK9OfbhGUlZvrJax.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131835ClcNAmzUnQ0sdaVp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">之前我们介绍过猫咪额头味道的喷雾，现在这个品牌又推出了猫咪手掌味的润手霜。虽然我家有三只猫，但我依然想象不出猫咪额头和手掌味到底是什么，据说是爆米花的味道一样。猫奴们可能会喜欢，购买戳<a href=\"http://www.felissimo.co.jp/neko/gcd649939/\">这里</a>。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131836brFkGAqcBiL7ps5z.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131836IgiCSJr8pnumKE5L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131837heP47XQSYOHI8K3p.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">这里有一个来自旧金山的包袋品牌 \r\n\r\nFuture Glory\r\n\r\n，需要提前预定，价格在 350 美元左右。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131837uGnzQET3AFrwWy0h.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131838QaEdJ3fNRoqCj0xK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071318389iS1VBLEoOqKyhuW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131839kriBnIzpPGf3LQOe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131839cYxztQvouPihLNJy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131840MTcWfXINiVu2Qloz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">Marc Jacobs 推出 Nudes 系列唇膏 ，裸色唇膏其实不像你想像的只有一种颜色，它还有棕裸、粉裸、桃裸等等。共有 7 色选择，每支为 30 美金。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131840b0dUizS3KDN7cwkT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071318414qlBLeFZCDAHM2zb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131841XEpGmC4fySaFV3ub.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">大热的运动品牌 Outdoor Voices，推出美利奴羊毛的运动装系列。 </p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131842EjhlxFJu40GcqdHm.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131842FaciuJ0vzlyxIthL.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131843YWenRKfp7C9l0F4L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071318439Umz8G2apTJ1csrW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071318446hWfb5oDeszY3BrU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131844nbBLisTFXdeNY3ak.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131845Bvpkj6Oe7lz3xELf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>现在流行这样的美甲，就是不涂满整个指甲。看起来还挺有趣的，尤其是那个在指甲不同位置点上小黑点的，虽然密恐患者可能会受不了。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131845vOxEGNw8Dzf75WU1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131846CVpF51q8KuUNxoJd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131846kOrNIdVwujTihRGE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131847tbOGc9xX4zLH62Ug.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131847h2NHJYq67CwiBuK1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131848GW7L1bXVeUvkc5aH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"> Stussy 的女装系列春夏新款，是典型的美国西海岸 grunge 风。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">  <figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131848tcKoiXxlFp4I3g12.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131849F6hbEQWqID43PUNy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131849R0s1qckXupyMdfE5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131849iZn0XAOEGJ26aS9y.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4988764\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131850joshfEUli0TW1NSO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607131850fOZUCjdJI4RspSul.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}